Development requires at least 20 [[File:Fuel.png|20px]], 10 [[File:Ammunition.png|20px]], 10 [[File:Steel.png|20px]], 110 [[File:Bauxite.png|20px]], with Bauxite as primary resource for a drop rate of 4%. No reports exist of successful development with Fuel/Steel or Ammo as primary resource.

